description:
Real-time synchronization, scheduled and auto backup of Windows PCs to QNAP NAS.

QNAP NetBak Replicator features real-time synchronization, scheduled and auto backup of the entire disk drives, documents, multimedia files and e-mails from multiple Windows PCs to QNAP NAS. It also supports backing up to a remote server via FTP and WebDAV over the Internet.
[Fixed Issues]
- Improved app security by fixing potential security vulnerability.
